  "why": "The paper describes differential testing across multiple ASR systems and uses failed cases as seeds for text transformation, but it does not demonstrate or measure whether fault-inducing inputs discovered on one model transfer to other independently trained models. There are no experiments, results, or explicit claims showing reuse of failure-inducing inputs from a surrogate to trigger failures in unseen target models, nor design choices explicitly aimed at discovering transferable failures.",
